descriptionHtml:
TO DOWNLOAD GO TO MIRRORS-use second mirror if first isnt working
if you like comment and thumbs up (or the equivalent for this website) 
if you want to edit this file feel free to do so but do not redistrubute without permission first
to edit find what file you would like to edit e.g if you want more hp find player.setav health 300 and change it to whatever you like, 
to use this mod place into: computer/os(C:)/program files (x86)/steam/steamapps/common/skyrim : and extract here 
open up skyrim make a new account (if you want, doesnt matter(make sure your not still in the tutorial when you use this mod))
open up console with tilde (~) found on the upper left below escape and type:bat everything
and HAVE FUN!!
if by request i will make a seperate file adding specific items (armour sets,weapons, misc)
